lisslo (0.3) walhalla; urgency=medium

  * Fix error in system interface.
    Avoid evaluating "/org/freedesktop/login1/session/self" in module scope
    which will fail with "GLib.Error: g-io-error-quark:
    GDBus.Error:System.Error.ENXIO: No such device or address" when run from
    system space.
    Side note: GLib.Error can not be chached in Python since it does not
    inherit "BaseException".
  * Ignore encoding errors

